        <div class="title-in">
        <p style='font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255,255,255)!important;'> 再小的个体，也可以因专业而伟大! </p>
        </div>
        
        <div   style="padding: 0;margin: 25px auto;" class="boxMain">
            <img src="/Public/hplus/img/login_logo.png" style="width: 110px;height: 110px;border-radius: 50%;display: block;margin:0 auto">
            <p class="m-t-md" style=" font-size: 20px; color: rgb(251,252,244);text-align: center;margin-top: 20px;">在这里共享商企平台</p>
            <form onsubmit="javascript:return false;" style="border: none;background: transparent;box-shadow: 0 0 0 transparent;padding-top: 0px;" >
            <div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control uname" name="username" id="username1" placeholder="手机号或者商户号" />
                <input type="password" class="form-control pword m-b" name="password" id="password1" placeholder="密码" style="margin-top: 0" />
            </div>
                
                <a href="/Business/Log/findpassword"  style="color: #fff;font-weight: 500">忘记密码了？</a>
                <button class="btn btn-success btn-block" onclick="javascript:loginAction();" style="margin-bottom: 15px;background: rgb(73,208,171);border: 1px solid rgb(73,208,171) ;font-weight: 500">立即登录</button>
                 <strong>还没有账户？ <a href="/Business/Log/check" style="color: #fff;font-weight: 500">立即注册 &raquo;</a></strong>
